Port-forward a common mcp-sentinel service

Usage:
  mcp-runtime sentinel port-forward [target] [flags]

Flags:
      --address string   Addresses to listen on (default "127.0.0.1")
  -h, --help             help for port-forward
      --port int         Local port to bind (defaults to the target service port)

Global Flags:
      --debug   Enable debug mode with structured error logging
